                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260112-98-victim583 t18260112-98-viclabel552"></join>. On the 12th of December the prisoner came, and called for half a pint of porter - he staid till the rest of the company had left the room, and then went away - one of the company went into the room again, and cried out, "The man has taken the candlestick;" I pursued, and took him with it, about four doors off.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. At the time I went into the house I was intoxicated.</p>
